    {
      "id": "c2-I-1",
      "number": "I-1",
      "topic": "平移抛物线与不等式",
      "topicTag": "二次函数",
      "humanVerified": false,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": true,
      "japanese": "$a > 0$。$y = \\dfrac{1}{4}x^2$ 平移后与 $x$ 轴交于 $(-2a, 0), (4a, 0)$，移动后方程 $y = f(x)$。\n\n(1) $f(x) = \\dfrac{\\fbox{A}}{\\fbox{B}}(x - \\fbox{C}\\,a)(x + \\fbox{D}\\,a)$。\n\n(2) $y \\le 10a^2$ 的 $x$ 范围：$x^2 - \\fbox{E}\\,ax - \\fbox{FG}\\,a^2 \\le 0$，即 $-\\fbox{H}\\,a \\le x \\le \\fbox{I}\\,a$。\n\n(3) 直线 $y = 10a$ 截 $y = f(x)$ 所得弦长 $= 10$。$\\fbox{J}\\sqrt{\\fbox{K}\\,a^2 + \\fbox{LM}\\,a} = 10$，故 $a = \\dfrac{\\fbox{N}}{\\fbox{O}}$。",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "(1) 两零点 $4a, -2a$，二次项系数 $1/4$；(2) 移项后开口向上区间；(3) 两交点 $x$ 距离 = 弦长。",
        "analysis": "$f(x) = (1/4)(x-4a)(x+2a) = (1/4)(x^2 - 2ax - 8a^2)$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1)",
            "content": "$f(x) = \\dfrac{1}{4}(x - 4a)(x + 2a)$。$\\fbox{A}=1, \\fbox{B}=4, \\fbox{C}=4, \\fbox{D}=2$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 不等式",
            "content": "$\\dfrac{1}{4}(x^2 - 2ax - 8a^2) \\le 10a^2 \\Rightarrow x^2 - 2ax - 48a^2 \\le 0$。$\\fbox{E}=2, \\fbox{FG}=48$。\n\n$(x - 8a)(x + 6a) \\le 0 \\Rightarrow -6a \\le x \\le 8a$。$\\fbox{H}=6, \\fbox{I}=8$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 弦长",
            "content": "$f(x) = 10a \\Rightarrow x^2 - 2ax - (8a^2 + 40a) = 0$。$|x_1 - x_2| = 2\\sqrt{9a^2 + 40a}$。$\\fbox{J}=2, \\fbox{K}=9, \\fbox{LM}=40$。\n\n$2\\sqrt{9a^2 + 40a} = 10 \\Rightarrow 9a^2 + 40a - 25 = 0 \\Rightarrow a = 5/9$。$\\fbox{NO}=59$。"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "ABCD=1442, EFG=248, HI=68, JKLM=2940, NO=59"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c2-I-2",
      "number": "I-2",
      "topic": "10阶楼梯走法计数",
      "topicTag": "组合",
      "humanVerified": false,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": true,
      "japanese": "$10$ 阶楼梯，每次 $1$ 阶或 $2$ 阶，$1$ 阶和 $2$ 阶都必至少 $1$ 次。\n\n(1) $2$ 阶可连续。(i) $2$ 阶 $3$ 次，$1$ 阶 $\\fbox{P}$ 次，方法数 $\\fbox{QR}$。(ii) 全部 $\\fbox{ST}$ 通。\n\n(2) $2$ 阶不连续。(i) $2$ 阶 $2$ 次，$1$ 阶 $\\fbox{U}$ 次，方法数 $\\fbox{VW}$。(ii) 全部 $\\fbox{XY}$ 通。",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "$2k + (10-2k) = 10$。$k \\in \\{1,2,3,4\\}$。",
        "analysis": "可连续：$C(n, k)$ 排列；不可连续：$C(n-k+1, k)$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 可连续",
            "content": "(i) $2\\cdot 3 + 1\\cdot 4 = 10$，$\\fbox{P}=4$。$\\binom{7}{3} = 35$。$\\fbox{QR}=35$。\n\n(ii) $\\binom{9}{1} + \\binom{8}{2} + \\binom{7}{3} + \\binom{6}{4} = 9+28+35+15 = 87$。$\\fbox{ST}=87$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 不连续",
            "content": "(i) $2\\cdot 2 + 1\\cdot 6 = 10$，$\\fbox{U}=6$。$\\binom{7}{2} = 21$。$\\fbox{VW}=21$。\n\n(ii) $\\binom{9}{1} + \\binom{7}{2} + \\binom{5}{3} + \\binom{3}{4} = 9 + 21 + 10 + 0 = 40$。$\\fbox{XY}=40$。"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "P=4, QR=35, ST=87, U=6, VW=21, XY=40"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c2-II-1",
      "number": "II-1",
      "topic": "数列前 n 项和与通项",
      "topicTag": "数列",
      "humanVerified": false,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": true,
      "japanese": "$S_n = \\dfrac{n^2 - 17n}{4}$ 是 $\\{a_n\\}$ 的前 $n$ 项和。$b_n = a_n \\cdot a_{n+5}$。\n\n(1) $a_n = \\fbox{A}$，$b_n = \\fbox{B}$，$T_n = \\sum_{k=1}^n b_k = \\fbox{C}$。\n选项：⓪ $(n-7)/2$ ① $(n-9)/2$ ② $(n-11)/2$ ③ $(n^2-12n+27)/4$ ④ $(n^2-13n+36)/4$ ⑤ $(n^2-14n+45)/4$ ⑥ $n(n^2-17n+83)/12$ ⑦ $n(n^2-17n+89)/12$ ⑧ $n(n^2-18n+83)/12$ ⑨ $n(n^2-18n+89)/12$\n\n(2) $n \\le \\fbox{D}$ 或 $\\fbox{EF} \\le n$ 时 $b_n > 0$；$\\fbox{G} \\le n \\le \\fbox{H}$ 时 $b_n < 0$。$T_n$ 最小在 $n = \\fbox{I}, \\fbox{J}, \\fbox{K}$（$\\fbox{I} < \\fbox{J} < \\fbox{K}$），值 $= \\fbox{L}$。",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "$a_n = S_n - S_{n-1}$；$b_n$ 二次因式分解后查正负。",
        "analysis": "$T_n$ 最小在 $b_n$ 累积负值结束之处。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1)",
            "content": "$a_n = (2n - 18)/4 = (n - 9)/2$。$\\fbox{A}=①$。\n\n$b_n = (n-9)(n-4)/4 = (n^2 - 13n + 36)/4$。$\\fbox{B}=④$。\n\n$T_n = \\dfrac{1}{4}\\left[\\dfrac{n(n+1)(2n+1)}{6} - \\dfrac{13n(n+1)}{2} + 36n\\right] = \\dfrac{n(n^2 - 18n + 89)}{12}$。$\\fbox{C}=⑨$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 正负与最小值",
            "content": "$b_n > 0 \\Leftrightarrow n \\le 3$ 或 $n \\ge 10$。$\\fbox{DEF}=310$。$b_n < 0 \\Leftrightarrow 5 \\le n \\le 8$。$\\fbox{GH}=58$。\n\n$T_1 = 6, T_8 = 8\\cdot 9/12 = 6, T_9 = 9\\cdot 8/12 = 6$。最小 $= 6$ 在 $n = 1, 8, 9$。$\\fbox{I}=1, \\fbox{J}=8, \\fbox{K}=9, \\fbox{L}=6$。"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "A=1, B=4, C=9, DEF=310, GH=58, I=1, J=8, K=9, L=6"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c2-II-2",
      "number": "II-2",
      "topic": "复数极形式与 8 次方程根",
      "topicTag": "复数",
      "humanVerified": false,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": true,
      "japanese": "(1) $8 + 8\\sqrt 3 i$ 极形式：$\\fbox{MN}\\left(\\cos\\dfrac{\\pi}{\\fbox{O}} + i\\sin\\dfrac{\\pi}{\\fbox{P}}\\right)$。\n\n(2) $z^4 = 8 + 8\\sqrt 3 i$，$0 \\le \\arg z < 2\\pi$ 共 $4$ 解。$|z| = \\fbox{Q}$。辐角小到大记 $z_1, z_2, z_3, z_4$，$\\arg\\dfrac{z_1 z_2 z_3}{z_4} = \\dfrac{\\pi}{\\fbox{R}}$。\n\n(3) $w^8 - 16w^4 + 256 = 0$，$0 \\le \\arg w < 2\\pi$ 共 $8$ 解 $w_1, \\ldots, w_8$。其中 $4$ 个与 (2) 的 $z_k$ 重合：$w_{\\fbox{S}} = z_1$, $w_{\\fbox{T}} = z_2$, $w_{\\fbox{U}} = z_3$, $w_{\\fbox{V}} = z_4$。\n\n$w_1 w_8 = \\fbox{W}$，$w_3 w_4 = \\fbox{XY}\\,i$。",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "$|8+8\\sqrt 3 i| = 16$；$w^4 = 8 \\pm 8\\sqrt 3 i$。",
        "analysis": "二次方程分解得两组四次根，共 $8$ 解。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1)",
            "content": "$|8 + 8\\sqrt 3 i| = 16$，$\\arg = \\pi/3$。$16(\\cos\\pi/3 + i\\sin\\pi/3)$。$\\fbox{MN}=16, \\fbox{OP}=33$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) $z^4$ 根",
            "content": "$|z| = 2$。$\\fbox{Q}=2$。辐角 $\\pi/12, 7\\pi/12, 13\\pi/12, 19\\pi/12$。$\\arg(z_1 z_2 z_3/z_4) = (1+7+13-19)\\pi/12 = \\pi/6$。$\\fbox{R}=6$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 8 次方程",
            "content": "$w^4 = (16 \\pm \\sqrt{-768})/2 = 8 \\pm 8\\sqrt 3 i$。\n\n$8 + 8\\sqrt 3 i$ 给辐角 $\\pi/12, 7\\pi/12, 13\\pi/12, 19\\pi/12$（即 $z_k$）；$8 - 8\\sqrt 3 i$ 给 $5\\pi/12, 11\\pi/12, 17\\pi/12, 23\\pi/12$。\n\n排序：$\\pi/12, 5\\pi/12, 7\\pi/12, 11\\pi/12, 13\\pi/12, 17\\pi/12, 19\\pi/12, 23\\pi/12$。$w_1 = z_1, w_3 = z_2, w_5 = z_3, w_7 = z_4$。$\\fbox{STUV}=1357$。\n\n$w_1 w_8$：$\\arg$ 和 $= 2\\pi$，模 $= 4$。$w_1 w_8 = 4$。$\\fbox{W}=4$。\n\n$w_3 w_4$：$\\arg$ 和 $= 3\\pi/2$，模 $= 4$。$w_3 w_4 = 4(0 - i) = -4i$。$\\fbox{XY}=-4$。"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "MN=16, OP=33, Q=2, R=6, STUV=1357, W=4, XY=-4"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c2-III-1",
      "number": "III",
      "topic": "两切线夹角的正切",
      "topicTag": "微分·切线",
      "humanVerified": false,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": true,
      "japanese": "$f(x) = x^3 - 4x + 4$。$\\ell$ 在 $A(-1, 7)$ 处切线；$m$ 是从 $B(0, -12)$ 作的切线。$\\ell, m$ 交于 $C$。夹角 $\\theta \\in (0, \\pi/2)$。\n\n(1) $f'(x) = \\fbox{A}\\,x^{\\fbox{B}} - \\fbox{C}$。$\\ell$ 斜率 $\\fbox{DE}$，$\\ell: y = \\fbox{DE}\\,x + \\fbox{F}$。\n\n(2) $m$ 切点 $x = a$。$m: y = (\\fbox{G}\\,a^{\\fbox{H}} - \\fbox{I})x - \\fbox{J}\\,a^{\\fbox{K}} + \\fbox{L}$。$m$ 过 $B$：$a = \\fbox{M}$，$m: y = \\fbox{N}\\,x - \\fbox{OP}$。$C = (\\fbox{Q}, \\fbox{R})$。\n\n(3) $\\tan\\alpha = \\fbox{ST}$，$\\tan\\beta = \\fbox{U}$，$\\tan\\theta = \\dfrac{\\fbox{V}}{\\fbox{W}}$。",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "切线 $y = f'(a)(x-a) + f(a)$；夹角 $\\tan(\\beta-\\alpha)$。",
        "analysis": "$y = (3a^2 - 4)x - 2a^3 + 4$；过 $(0, -12) \\Rightarrow a^3 = 8$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) $\\ell$",
            "content": "$f'(x) = 3x^2 - 4$。$\\fbox{ABC}=324$。$f'(-1) = -1$。$\\fbox{DE}=-1$。$\\ell: y = -x + 6$。$\\fbox{F}=6$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) $m$ 与 $C$",
            "content": "$m: y = (3a^2 - 4)x - 2a^3 + 4$。$\\fbox{GHI}=324, \\fbox{JKL}=234$。\n\n$-2a^3 + 4 = -12 \\Rightarrow a = 2$。$\\fbox{M}=2$。$m: y = 8x - 12$。$\\fbox{NOP}=812$。\n\n$-x + 6 = 8x - 12 \\Rightarrow x = 2, y = 4$。$C(2, 4)$。$\\fbox{QR}=24$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 夹角",
            "content": "$\\tan\\alpha = -1$，$\\tan\\beta = 8$。$\\fbox{ST}=-1, \\fbox{U}=8$。\n\n$\\tan(\\beta - \\alpha) = (8+1)/(1 - 8) = -9/7$。$\\theta \\in (0,\\pi/2)$ 取绝对值：$\\tan\\theta = 9/7$。$\\fbox{VW}=97$。"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "ABC=324, DE=-1, F=6, GHI=324, JKL=234, M=2, NOP=812, QR=24, ST=-1, U=8, VW=97"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c2-IV-1",
      "number": "IV",
      "topic": "三角函数之和的面积",
      "topicTag": "三角·积分",
      "humanVerified": false,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": true,
      "japanese": "$f(x) = \\sin x + \\dfrac{\\sin 2x}{2} + \\dfrac{\\sin 3x}{3}$（$0 \\le x \\le \\pi$）。证 $0 < x < \\pi$ 时 $f(x) > 0$ 并求 $S$。\n\n(1) $f'(x) = (\\fbox{A}\\cos^2 x - \\fbox{B})(\\fbox{C}\\cos x + \\fbox{D})$。零点 $x = \\dfrac{\\pi}{\\fbox{E}}, \\dfrac{\\fbox{F}}{\\fbox{G}}\\pi, \\dfrac{\\fbox{H}}{\\fbox{I}}\\pi$。\n\n增减：$[0, \\pi/J]$：$\\fbox{K}$；$[\\pi/J, L\\pi/M]$：$\\fbox{N}$；$[L\\pi/M, O\\pi/P]$：$\\fbox{Q}$；$[O\\pi/P, \\pi]$：$\\fbox{R}$。选项：⓪ 增加 ① 减少\n\n$f(L\\pi/M) = \\dfrac{\\sqrt{\\fbox{S}}}{\\fbox{T}} > 0$。\n\n(2) $S = \\dfrac{\\fbox{UV}}{\\fbox{W}}$。",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "$f' = \\cos x + \\cos 2x + \\cos 3x$ 因式分解。",
        "analysis": "代入 $\\cos 2x, \\cos 3x$ 得 $(2\\cos^2 x - 1)(2\\cos x + 1)$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 增减与极小",
            "content": "$f'(x) = 4\\cos^3 x + 2\\cos^2 x - 2\\cos x - 1 = (2\\cos^2 x - 1)(2\\cos x + 1)$。$\\fbox{ABCD}=2121$。\n\n零点：$\\cos x = \\pm 1/\\sqrt 2$ 得 $\\pi/4, 3\\pi/4$；$\\cos x = -1/2$ 得 $2\\pi/3$。排序 $\\pi/4 < 2\\pi/3 < 3\\pi/4$。$\\fbox{E}=4, \\fbox{FG}=23, \\fbox{HI}=34$。\n\n增减：$[0, \\pi/4]$ 增；$[\\pi/4, 2\\pi/3]$ 减；$[2\\pi/3, 3\\pi/4]$ 增；$[3\\pi/4, \\pi]$ 减。$\\fbox{K}=0, \\fbox{LM}=23, \\fbox{N}=1, \\fbox{OP}=34, \\fbox{Q}=0, \\fbox{R}=1$。\n\n$f(2\\pi/3) = \\sqrt 3/2 + \\sin(4\\pi/3)/2 + 0 = \\sqrt 3/2 - \\sqrt 3/4 = \\sqrt 3/4$。$\\fbox{ST}=34$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 面积",
            "content": "$S = \\left[-\\cos x - \\dfrac{\\cos 2x}{4} - \\dfrac{\\cos 3x}{9}\\right]_0^\\pi = (1 - 1/4 + 1/9) - (-1 - 1/4 - 1/9) = 2 + 2/9 = 20/9$。$\\fbox{UVW}=209$。"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "ABCD=2121, E=4, FG=23, HI=34, J=4, K=0, LM=23, N=1, OP=34, Q=0, R=1, ST=34, UVW=209"
      }
    }
